# Google Civic Information API key
# Required for the "Find Your Lawmakers" feature.
#
# Steps to get a key:
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/
# 2. Create or select a project
# 3. Enable the "Google Civic Information API"
# 4. Create an API key under "APIs & Services > Credentials"
# 5. (Recommended) Restrict the key to your domain under "API restrictions"
#
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your key:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# Note: Vite exposes any variable prefixed with VITE_ to the browser bundle.
# Restrict your key by HTTP referrer in Google Cloud Console to prevent misuse.

VITE_GOOGLE_CIVIC_API_KEY=your_google_civic_api_key_here
